WEBVTT

00:00.242 --> 00:01.906
Previously on "Bitten"...

00:02.164 --> 00:05.303
- What was that?
- Uh, wiring. It's fine.

00:05.328 --> 00:06.795
They know where we are. We have to move,

00:06.797 --> 00:09.064
- find another base.
- I have a place already.

00:09.066 --> 00:11.764
Katia and Alexei saw
their mother torn apart

00:11.789 --> 00:13.722
by a wolf with one red eye.

00:13.724 --> 00:14.757
Roman's assassins.

00:14.891 --> 00:16.690
It wasn't a dream, was it?

00:16.692 --> 00:19.593
That boy, he was
changing into something.

00:19.595 --> 00:22.896
God, did I see him...
change into a wolf?

00:22.898 --> 00:24.297
This is my responsibility.

00:24.299 --> 00:27.033
I'll figure it all out.

00:27.035 --> 00:29.603
What's happening there?

00:29.605 --> 00:31.104
I spoke to Jorge,

00:31.106 --> 00:32.973
he told me that you had him track Roman.

00:32.975 --> 00:35.409
He found a lot of credit cards
that lead to Southern Ontario.

00:35.411 --> 00:38.044
- Are you coming back?
- I am going to go after Roman.

00:38.046 --> 00:40.513
This is from the Russian wolf.
It's infected.

00:40.515 --> 00:41.982
I can turn around. We can be there

00:41.984 --> 00:43.383
in an hour and a half, tops.

00:43.385 --> 00:44.885
- Rachel isn't answering?
- No.

00:44.887 --> 00:47.653
- Go to Rachel's.
- I found this at the front gate.

00:49.892 --> 00:52.359
That's Marsten.

00:52.361 --> 00:55.628
Please, enough...
enough!

